---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ImgSlot from '../components/ImgSlot.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About · AI Powered Events Indonesia"
  description="Founder Ross Power and AI Powered Events Indonesia. Building Bali's leading in-person AI community. Human, Artificial, Divine."
>
  <Hero
    eyebrow="About"
    title="Become AI powered.<br>Remain human."
    lead="AI Powered Events Indonesia is building Bali's leading in-person AI community, educating, entertaining and inspiring entrepreneurs through world-class gatherings."
    primaryCta={{ href: '/waitlist', label: 'Join waitlist' }}
    secondaryCta={{ href: '/sponsors', label: 'Become a sponsor' }}
    compact
  />

  <section class="section-light" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="grid g2" style="gap:52px;align-items:center">
        <ImgSlot label="Ross Power portrait" minHeight="440px" />
        <div>
          <p class="kicker">The Founder</p>
          <h2>Ross Power.</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:20px">Founder and Director, AI Powered Events Indonesia. The connector between Bali's builders, the world's best teachers, and the partners who power them.</p>
          <p class="text-soft" style="font-size:15.5px;margin-bottom:16px">Ross led 100+ design-thinking workshops at Accenture, built through blockchain startups and product leadership roles, and served as Head of Product at a NYSE-listed education company before founding AI Powered, where he now teaches entrepreneurs to run AI-powered businesses through cohort programmes (including Claude Programme 3.0), a growing community, and hands-on education.</p>
          <p class="text-soft" style="font-size:15.5px">Based in Bali, Ross is building the bridge between the island's 50,000-strong entrepreneur community and the global AI economy, with events as the connective tissue: educate, entertain, inspire.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-light">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="kicker">The Entity</p>
      <h2>AI Powered Events Indonesia.</h2>
      <p class="lead mb-44">We're building Bali's leading in-person AI community brand. Events that blend practical business education with human connection and conscious living.</p>
      <div class="grid g3">
        <div class="card">
          <p class="pillar-num">01 · Human</p>
          <h3>Human</h3>
          <p class="text-soft">Connection is the foundation. Offline, in-person experiences. Music, arts and creativity woven through every gathering. Real rooms, real relationships. In a world of infinite content, the scarce resource is presence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="pillar-num">02 · Artificial</p>
          <h3>Artificial</h3>
          <p class="text-soft">AI is handing back the most valuable asset an entrepreneur has: time. We teach the practical power of AI to take time back, build leaner businesses, and create a more meaningful life outside the screen. Not theory. Tactics. Not hype. Leverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="pillar-num">03 · Divine</p>
          <h3>Divine</h3>
          <p class="text-soft">Spiritual connectedness and consciousness. The dimension Bali does better than anywhere on earth. Our events honour the island's unique energy: the space to think clearly, connect deeply, and return home changed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="grid g2" style="gap:52px;align-items:center">
        <div>
          <p class="kicker">The Bigger Play</p>
          <h2>Backed by Bali's boldest project.</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:20px">We're in pursuit of something bigger than a conference: a collaboration with the Indonesian government and the island's new Special Economic Zone.</p>
          <p class="text-soft" style="margin-bottom:16px"><b style="color:#fff">Kura Kura Bali</b> is a 100-hectare innovation and financial hub on Serangan Island, being developed as Indonesia's answer to Dubai's financial districts. Focused on digital technology, creative industries, luxury tourism and international finance, with income-tax holidays, VAT exemptions and duty-free import incentives for investors.</p>
          <p class="text-soft">Hosting our flagship event inside the SEZ positions AI Powered Bali at the front of Indonesia's push to make Bali a global business destination, alongside government, investors and the region's innovation economy.</p>
        </div>
        <ImgSlot label="Kura Kura Bali aerial" minHeight="440px" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-light">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="kicker">The Roadmap</p>
      <h2>Two events. One movement.</h2>
      <div class="timeline" style="margin-top:14px">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="label">Step 1 · September 2026</div>
          <h3>The Ignition · Canggu</h3>
          <p class="text-soft" style="font-size:15.5px">A 1-day event and afterparty bringing together speakers and builders from across Bali on all three pillars. Proof of concept, first content engine, and the founding community for April.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card featured">
          <div class="label" style="color:var(--accent)">Step 2 · April 2027</div>
          <h3>The Flagship · 2 to 3 days</h3>
          <p class="text-soft" style="font-size:15.5px">700 to 1,000 entrepreneurs. International speaker line-up. Government and SEZ collaboration. Workshops by day, music and experiences by night.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark">
    <div class="wrap text-center" style="max-width:720px">
      <p class="kicker">Join us</p>
      <h2>Be part of the movement.</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin:0 auto 30px">Whether you're attending, speaking or partnering, we'd love to hear from you.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas" style="justify-content:center">
        <a class="btn-white" href="/waitlist">Join waitlist</a>
        <a class="btn-outline" href="/sponsors">Become a sponsor</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
